{"tid":1553491,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"（再開）全城唔知係咪最大既義教防身術班上線啦","createTime":"2019-09-08T15:32:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-13T08:47:47.000Z","uid":115955,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"7c6c085b8202d05d7681b4bc53aa8916e5447ccb","tid":1553491,"uid":115955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T15:32:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實我由7月開始都有搞，不過嗰時就好低調咁搞，不過其實宜加啲狗都痴撚左線<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />人人都最少要識啲要練習過<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n主要係教大家有一個意識當有襲擊的時候。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我發現好多人都冇一個反應去準備應付一啲突如其來的事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，最少要有個概念要點預防，同如果真係畀人襲擊緊，應該點樣諗去走或保護自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">逢星期四<br />\n2000-2130<br />\n防身及體能<br />\n最多20人一班<br />\n跑馬地馬場</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">有興趣，不如可以留tg</span><br />\n之後有人會搵你架啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我重申<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我唔係教你地點樣去勇武，係教你點樣保護自己既概念<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一日未上警車一日都要嘗試走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />反正都畀狗打同告架啦，一定要拼命走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n祝武運昌通"},{"pid":"f7e03b89a828dba64f30541f5b8eb846b7a0401b","tid":1553491,"uid":115955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T15:33:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e20ce5562b75e65ac2a657b0f493f98aad07ffab","tid":1553491,"uid":115955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T15:33:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"44e088e0471cda0c8b30c650bb66fce4d043e4b8","tid":1553491,"uid":115955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T15:33:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2b8487d1fcebb1547f9ffe52a9298ccbdb02e343","tid":1553491,"uid":115955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T15:34:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0107fcc06e7db63f979b33ed6cdf33c321420c96","tid":1553491,"uid":115955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T15:34:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6900a9317ac3748dfa1e6f3cd7a52fea6338b612","tid":1553491,"uid":115955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T15:34:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"53f9e51d4f882b10a40003ca4265e1db29a12399","tid":1553491,"uid":115955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T15:35:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6aca01723021d481f5472126fe452a9f368a76dd","tid":1553491,"uid":115955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T15:36:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a8b4fdda7666d9bafb387693c4974f2c9e0ad00a","tid":1553491,"uid":115955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T15:37:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"61cdeb50376d31f4e99b4716e8d093d6ca233a7b","tid":1553491,"uid":282321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T15:37:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae28ef4fc49587b1c980d3a642473b901ae39fb2","tid":1553491,"uid":115955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T15:39:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8e1f1c21437